    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sao Paulo, 22nd century, <strong>technology</strong> has merged with concepts that would be considered <strong>magic</strong> in our time. This breakthrough could greatly increase quality of life and the lifespan of the population. However, after starting the human trials a few people starting developing strange and severe side effects from an unknown source that can even be responsible for their deaths. Is there someone behind it? What is their agenda? Will you be able to uncover what is behind this? <strong>Can you stop it?</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>O.U.T.T. is a 3D turn-based puzzle-adventure game with a deep narrative, multiple endings, challenging puzzles with a retro futuristic cyber soulpunk aesthetic in a pre-dystopic future.</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Beware the enemies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat or escape several enemies with different behaviors including extra planar entities. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839020/extras/782e1ab9043b0271df735aaee3c57074.poster.avif?t=1771873356\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839020/extras/782e1ab9043b0271df735aaee3c57074.webm?t=1771873356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839020/extras/782e1ab9043b0271df735aaee3c57074.mp4?t=1771873356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenging puzzles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use lever, buttons, light emitters, mirrors and sensor, and even hack computers with a 3D tetris-like game to get your way around the levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839020/extras/c21faa19f2e2a04650387e693bf1dc83.poster.avif?t=1771873356\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839020/extras/c21faa19f2e2a04650387e693bf1dc83.webm?t=1771873356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839020/extras/c21faa19f2e2a04650387e693bf1dc83.mp4?t=1771873356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Deep narrative with multiple endings</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All interactions are meaningful and can change a future outcome in the game that unfolds each level and on the comic-style cutscenes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839020/extras/fdf56bd9feb49ac1b53d7fb7beb45daa.poster.avif?t=1771873356\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839020/extras/fdf56bd9feb49ac1b53d7fb7beb45daa.webm?t=1771873356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839020/extras/fdf56bd9feb49ac1b53d7fb7beb45daa.mp4?t=1771873356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key features: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multilayered puzzle for challenging yet fair levels;,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rich narrative with multiple endings;,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several kinds of enemies, including extra planar entities;,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Highlight mode to help the player understand the puzzle easier that que be tuned on and off with one button.,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play at your own pace.</p></li></ul>",
